Description: Pink sandstone stela; scene of Amenhotep I and Ahmose-Nefertari(depicted twice) offering to Horus of Miam; seven rows of Hieroglyphic text below.
Curator's comments: Published: Klug, Koeniglichen Stelen (Mon Aeg 8, 2002): 52-4, Abb. 3
Associated names: Named in inscription & portrayed: Amenhotep I
Named in inscription & portrayed: Horus of Miam
